{"type":"message","id":"b36eade8","parentId":"0d0c1cbc","timestamp":"2026-04-28T08:57:52.532Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_bt0608536czj_2","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"Alex Finn YouTube channel all videos list\",\n  \"provider\": \"brave\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 932,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"brave\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d0dae3e12508303c\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAlex Finn - YouTube\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d0dae3e12508303c\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.youtube.com/@AlexFinnOfficial/videos\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d70dcae4da2ab6a0\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n<strong>The number 1 vibe coding channel on Youtube</strong>. I&#x27;ll teach you how to use Claude Code, Codex, and AI even if you&#x27;ve never used them before! I built a $300,000 a year AI app without writing a single line of code.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d70dcae4da2ab6a0\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.youtube.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"bd19c9c202669197\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAlex Finn\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"bd19c9c202669197\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://m.youtube.com/channel/UCfQNB91qRP_5ILeu_S_bSkg/videos/videos\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"5846a7824fd71e34\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nShare your videos with friends, family, and the world\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"5846a7824fd71e34\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"m.youtube.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d43ae27bf74c054b\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAlex Finn — Grokipedia\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d43ae27bf74c054b\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://grokipedia.com/page/Alex_Finn\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"bd9e7f1da634c25a\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAlex Finn has played a significant role in democratizing AI coding education by targeting non-coders through his YouTube channel and associated initiatives, emphasizing intuitive, AI-assisted methods that lower barriers to entry in software development.[28] His tutorials, particularly those on workflows using Anthropic&#x27;s Claude, have garnered viewership, with videos such as &quot;Building a startup with Claude Code LIVE using my new workflow&quot; achieving approximately 2,800 views as of January 2026 and &quot;Using Claude Code to build startups LIVE!!!&quot; reaching approximately 1,600 views as of January 2026\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"bd9e7f1da634c25a\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"March 25, 2026\",\n      \"siteName\": \"grokipedia.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"80315dad407443ef\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAlex Finn (@AlexFinn) / Posts / X\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"80315dad407443ef\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://x.com/AlexFinn\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"fee26ec648934273\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAlex Finn · @AlexFinn · · · Mar 17, 2025 · This is Mark Rober He spent years building one of the strongest reputations in social media. Loved by tens of millions of followers Yesterday he obliterated it all with one 18 minute video It&#x27;s a story of greed, deception, and cowardice Here&#x27;s the story of what happened: 4.5K ·\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"fee26ec648934273\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"March 9, 2021\",\n      \"siteName\": \"x.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"edc392852ebf1d54\\\">>>\\nSource: W