lding your app now in Claude Code, you just hand this off to it, and it now has the full dashboard and can take all of this and implement it into your app. You now went from having AI slop to a fully designed, professionally built out design system exactly to your liking. If you want to take it further and you want to refine it from here, edit things, you can do that. You can go into your chat, say, change this, make this better, change this color, I like this, I don't like this, and make it even better for your taste. This is the system you need to be using. Combining Chad GPT image gen, which is bestin-class and has basically no limits whatsoever. using that for your exploration, refinement, moving it over to claw design so you can oneshot build out some incredible designs. This is claw design and if you learned anything at all, hit like down below. I'm going to do an entire workshop on this and build this out live and take all your questions inside the Vibe Coding Academy. Make sure to hit the link for that down below. It's the number one community in AI on planet Earth. You'll learn a ton. You'll master claw code, claw design, open claw, all that. Hit the link down there. Subscribe and turn on notifications if you haven't already. All I do is make amazing videos about AI. I live stream Monday, Wednesday, Friday, 11 a.m. Pacific. So, tune in for that as well. I hope you learned something here. I'm so eternally grateful you would spend your time with me and listen to my advice and hang out with me. It really means the world. Thank you so much. I love you all and I'll talk to you","cwd":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-rex"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777373075825}}
