r Integration (Vibe Coding):** OpenClaw fully integrated with Linear (project management). Assigns tasks to agents → agent pulls code from GitHub → completes task → creates PR. Massive vibe coding multiplier.\n1. **Insurance**: When one breaks (especially after updates), the other can fix it → keeps uptime near 100%\n**Compaction amnesia:** Before this system, compacting would make OpenClaw forget things from 5 seconds ago. With Obsidian integration, before every compaction it checks the vault to see what it was working on — compaction becomes unnoticeable.\n**Memory on demand:** Small projects worked on for 5 minutes, then abandoned for weeks — now OpenClaw can find them instantly months later via daily logs.","cwd":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-rex"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777373081907}}
