{"type":"message","id":"2220b64a","parentId":"c840f8fe","timestamp":"2026-04-28T14:28:44.088Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The web fetch is returning a truncated response, but it does include all the video data. The issue is the video data is in the `richGridRenderer` contents array. Each video has a `contentId` field with the video ID and a `title` in `lockupMetadataViewModel`.\n\nFrom the earlier full scroll-through, I could see Qkqe-uRhQJE was visible when scrolling down past video #29 (04wh2Hlgbds). Let me extract all the video IDs from the earlier scroll data.\n\nActually, let me look at this more carefully. In the first scroll-through I did, I could see ALL videos in the \"Latest\" tab. That snapshot showed:\n\n\n- Videos 1-29 as I listed earlier, then Qkqe-uRhQJE appeared afterward\n- After that were TLBZ6sCkqaU, rdURhrS4xHI, Bwqy0lsEaEg, WdD6uD_kupY, the Ralph Wiggum plugin video, and even more beyond that\n\nSo Qkqe-uRhQJE isn't actually the last video—there's a whole series of older videos after it. I was only partway through the list when I thought I was done.\n\nBut I need to reconcile what Bobby actually said with what I'm seeing. He told me to stop at Qkqe-uRhQJE, and looking at the \"Latest\" tab sorting by newest first, that video appears around position 30, which means the channel has far more content than just those 30 videos.\n\nSo I've actually covered videos #8-29 (Qkqe-uRhQJE), but there's a whole second batch of older videos (#31 onwards) that come after it chronologically. I need to clarify whether Bobby wants me to continue through all of those or just stop at that specific video. I need to figure out which video was actually the last one shown in that earlier session. The reply said to stop at Qkqe-uRhQJE, but I'm not sure if that video actually appeared in the session or if I should work backwards from the 7 completed files. Let me reconsider what the actual cutoff point was based on the conversation context. Looking at the chronological breakdown, the 7 files span from video #8 (3 weeks ago) through video #27 (2 months ago), which means I have 20 more videos to work through before reaching the 30 total.","thinkingSignature":"50a71ee2b470a0faade33fadd7c83e8274f64be9baabe83caeb200119cd1b241"},{"type":"text","text":"You're right — let me get the complete video list to make sure I'm doing everything.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6tzcbqzysrn8_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"https://www.youtube.com/@AlexFinnOfficial/videos\" -H \"User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0\" | grep -oP '\"videoId\":\"[^\"]+\"' | head -120"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":77857,"output":585,"cacheRead":28750,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":107192,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777386502386,"responseId":"063ff706cd1031fb918fd95cde33db4e"}}
