{"type":"message","id":"f8138dcc","parentId":"62eaf534","timestamp":"2026-04-28T14:40:18.267Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_7q6m0x0jl4zp_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Total files:\n      24\n\nAll files:\n2026-04-28 - 100 hours of OpenClaw lessons in 35 minutes - Alex Finn.md\n2026-04-28 - 5 OpenClaw use cases that will actually improve your life - Alex Finn.md\n2026-04-28 - 5 OpenClaw use cases that will make you a productivity MACHINE - Alex Finn.md\n2026-04-28 - 5 insane ClawdBot uses cases you need to do immediately - Alex Finn.md\n2026-04-28 - 6 OpenClaw use cases I promise will change your life - Alex Finn.md\n2026-04-28 - Anthropic just blocked OpenClaw. Here's what you need to do immediately.md\n2026-04-28 - Claude Code Mobile just changed AI coding forever (Remote Control) - Alex Finn.md\n2026-04-28 - Claude Opus 4.6 is a MASSIVE upgrade for ClawdBot and Claude Code (full guide) - Alex Finn.md\n2026-04-28 - Claude Opus 4.6 — Greatest model for OpenClaw ever - Alex Finn.md\n2026-04-28 - DO NOT use a VPS for OpenClaw (major warning) - Alex Finn.md\n2026-04-28 - Did Hermes Agent just kill OpenClaw (full guide).md\n2026-04-28 - How to build an army of OpenClaw agents - Alex Finn.md\n2026-04-28 - How to make ClawdBot 10x better (5 easy steps) - Alex Finn.md\n2026-04-28 - How to run ClawdBot for DIRT CHEAP - Alex Finn.md\n2026-04-28 - I just spent $20,000 on OpenClaw. Here's why... - Alex Finn.md\n2026-04-28 - MASSIVE CLAUDE CODE LEAK! THIS CHANGES EVERYTHING!.md\n2026-04-28 - OpenClaw is 100x better with this tool (Mission Control) - Alex Finn.md\n2026-04-28 - OpenClaw is the most powerful AI tool I've ever used in my life. Here's how to set it up - Alex Finn.md\n2026-04-28 - The only OpenClaw tutorial you'll ever need (March 2026 edition) - Alex Finn.md\n2026-04-28 - This is the CHEAPEST and EASIEST way to set up ClawdBot - Alex Finn.md\n2026-04-28 - Why you NEED to be running local AI models (FULL beginner