{"type":"message","id":"d7b90ab0","parentId":"75f7ede0","timestamp":"2026-04-28T14:52:33.755Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me give Bobby a summary of what I created and ask if he has any questions.","thinkingSignature":"24130171e770f4b0400ea9ad9ec4b36a0a6875bc25909fa272adb03388fe8ff2"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nDone! Created `master-summary.md` at `~/Desktop/SecondBrain/Research/alex-finn/master-summary.md`\n\nIt covers everything organized into clear sections:\n\n- **What OpenClaw is** and why it's a game-changer\n- **Setup** (installation, hardware, messaging services)\n- **Brain & Muscles architecture** (how to use the right model for each task)\n- **Cost optimization** (the heartbeat trap, budget setups under $20/month)\n- **Memory configuration** (the two settings that make it 100x better)\n- **Pro techniques** (brain dump, expectation setting, reverse prompting)\n- **Building tooling** (task boards, CRM, mission control dashboards)\n- **Multi-agent teams**\n- **Security & account risk**\n- **Complete use case list**\n- **Quick start checklist**\n\nNo questions from me — I think I covered everything from the 31 videos. Does this capture what you were looking for, or is there anything you'd like me to add, reorganize, or go deeper on?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2833,"output":235,"cacheRead":65344,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68412,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777387950755,"responseId":"063ffcae74eeb93aca0e57cc8d44fdb7"}}
