{"type":"message","id":"0a8ebfd6","parentId":"e28b6c0f","timestamp":"2026-04-29T00:21:13.410Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Oh interesting! Bobby is working with Dean on an OpenClaw guide that he can sell. So the \"product\" right now is an OpenClaw guide/course. That's very meta - he's using what he's learning from Alex Finn's videos to create his own product.\n\nLet me ask some good questions to understand what he needs specifically for this guide project.","thinkingSignature":"0b50b4293fda2840ccb16d518f9c146df72711a6b642333714e48196e810ff6c"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nOh that's actually perfect — you're literally doing what Alex Finn teaches. Using OpenClaw to create something sellable. 🔥\n\nSo here's my question for this:\n\n**What stage is the guide in?** Like, are you still figuring out WHAT to include in it, or do you have the outline done and you're now working on the content?\n\nThat'll tell me where to focus our conversation — whether we should talk about:\n- How to structure and organize the guide\n- How to use OpenClaw to RESEARCH and WRITE the content faster\n- How to package and sell it (pricing, platform, etc.)\n\nWhich bucket are you in right now?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":69944,"output":206,"cacheRead":224,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70374,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777422067452,"responseId":"064081f32ff3e792a00a5f7a331fe825"}}
