{"type":"message","id":"7ba89550","parentId":"d3646076","timestamp":"2026-04-29T00:42:05.467Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_yqoow9dsy3ia_1","toolName":"sessions_history","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:telegram:direct:8212808444\",\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"okay then how much would i have after another months rent payment?\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1777418703394,\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"cb6e2306\",\n        \"seq\": 164\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"$2,819 - $1,850 = $969\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_function_8mqxf9hw60we_1\",\n          \"name\": \"exec\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"command\": \"cat >> ~/Desktop/Moving/UHAUL_COST_NOTES.md << 'EOF'\\n\\n## After 2nd Month Rent\\n- After 1st month rent: $2,819\\n- Minus 2nd month rent ($1,850): -$1,850\\n- **Remaining after 2nd month: ~$969**\\n\\nEOF\\necho \\\"Done\\\"\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"minimax-portal\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1777418703456,\n      \"responseId\": \"064074cf09e7ff4f448de1a7340ec221\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"0802d47b\",\n        \"seq\": 165\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"$2,819 - $1,850 = $969.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"**$969** after second month's rent. Gets tight — you'd basically be banking on steady income coming in by then.\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"minimax-portal\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1777418707508,\n      \"responseId\": \"064074d3444c1aad4928ac7e66ee6b5f\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"b87de250\",\n        \"seq\": 167\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"my mom also said she would loan us 13,000 to help with creditcards and anything but illl pay her back with minimum payments of 411 every month until its done. i can choose to pay it earlier as well but note that. i want you to have another section in this case where i do have the 13,000. how much would i have 13,969?\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1777418776960,\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"22009b4e\",\n        \"seq\": 168\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"Bobby wants to add a section with the $13,000 loan from his mom. He asks if he'd have $13,969 with the $13,000 added.\\n\\nCurrent theoretical total after U-Haul and before rent: $4,669\\nWith mom's loan: $4,669 + $13,000 = $17,669\\n\\nWait, let me re-read. After U-Haul ($700) and earning goal ($4,000) and starting cash ($1,369), Bobby has $4,669.\\n\\nWith mom's loan of $13,000: $4,669 + $13,000 = $17,669\\n\\nAfter 1st month rent ($1,850): $17,669 - $1,850 = $15,819\\n\\n\\nAfter 2nd month rent ($1,850): $15,819 - $1,850 = $13,969\\n\\nSo yes, after two months he'd have $13,969 left, which matches what Bobby calculated.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_function_l2zeznjd3ban_1\",\n          \"name\": \"exec\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"command\": \"cat >> ~/Desktop/Moving/UHAUL_COST_NOTES.md << 'EOF'\\n\\n## WITH Mom's Loan ($13,000)\\n- Starting cash + earnings + U-Haul: $4,669\\n- Plus mom's loan: +$13,000\\n- **Total with loan (pre-rent): $17,669**\\n\\n- After 1st month rent: $17,669 - $1,850 = **$15,819**\\n- After 2nd month rent: $15,819 - $1,850 = **$13,969**\\n\\n## Mom's Loan Repayment Terms\\n- Loan amount: $13,000\\n- Minimum payment: $411/month\\n- Can pay earlier at any time\\n\\nEOF\\necho \\\"Done\\\"\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"minimax-portal\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1777418777022,\n      \"responseId\": \"0640751948205699eb83aab8ab6cbfe3\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"22638adf\",\n        \"seq\": 169\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"Let me confirm: $4,669 + $13,000 = $17,669. After 2 months rent ($1,850 × 2 = $3,700), $17,669 - $3,700 = $13,969. Yes that's correct.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"Yeah you got it — **$13,969** after 2 months rent with mom's loan included. The $13k makes a big difference. At $411/month minimum it takes about 32 months to pay off ($13,000 ÷ $411 ≈ 31.6 months).\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"minimax-portal\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1777418804986,\n      \"responseId\": \"064075357e6f110da411d7b25a630a07\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"9d60a3ff\",\n        \"seq\": 171\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"okay you can stop taking notes. thank you\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1777418893214,\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"fdb9e22b\",\n        \"seq\": 172\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"Bobby wants me to stop taking notes. All the info is already saved in the UHAUL_COST_NOTES.md file. I'll confirm and let him know the file has everything.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"All good. Everything is saved in `~/Desktop/Moving/UHAUL_COST_NOTES.md` — all your moving notes in one place. 🤖\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"minimax-portal\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1777418893276,\n      \"responseId\": \"0640758e60f810357c9960e09f710a2a\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"b1513960\",\n        \"seq\": 173\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"truncated\": true,\n  \"droppedMessages\": false,\n  \"contentTruncated\": true,\n  \"contentRedacted\": false,\n  \"bytes\": 4520\n}"}],"details":{"sessionKey":"agent:main:telegram:direct:8212808444","messages":[{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"okay then how much would i have after another months rent payment?"}],"timestamp":1777418703394,"__openclaw":{"id":"cb6e2306","seq":164}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"$2,819 - $1,850 = $969"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8mqxf9hw60we_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat >> ~/Desktop/Moving/UHAUL_COST_NOTES.md << 'EOF'\n\n## After 2nd Month Rent\n- After 1st month rent: $2,819\n- Minus 2nd month rent ($1,850): -$1,850\n- **Remaining after 2nd month: ~$969**\n\nEOF\necho \"Done\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777418703456,"responseId":"064074cf09e7ff4f448de1a7340ec221","__openclaw":{"id":"0802d47b","seq":165}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"$2,819 - $1,850 = $969."},{"type":"text","text":"**$969** after second month's rent. Gets tight — you'd basically be banking on steady income coming in by then."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777418707508,"responseId":"064074d3444c1aad4928ac7e66ee6b5f","__openclaw":{"id":"b87de250","seq":167}},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"my mom also said she would loan us 13,000 to help with creditcards and anything but illl pay her back with minimum payments of 411 every month until its done. i can choose to pay it earlier as well but note that. i want you to have another section in this case where i do have the 13,000. how much would i have 13,969?"}],"timestamp":1777418776960,"__openclaw":{"id":"22009b4e","seq":168}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby wants to add a section with the $13,000 loan from his mom. He asks if he'd have $13,969 with the $13,000 added.\n\nCurrent theoretical total after U-Haul and before rent: $4,669\nWith mom's loan: $4,669 + $13,000 = $17,669\n\nWait, let me re-read. After U-Haul ($700) and earning goal ($4,000) and starting cash ($1,369), Bobby has $4,669.\n\nWith mom's loan of $13,000: $4,669 + $13,000 = $17,669\n\nAfter 1st month rent ($1,850): $17,669 - $1,850 = $15,819\n\n\nAfter 2nd month rent ($1,850): $15,819 - $1,850 = $13,969\n\nSo yes, after two months he'd have $13,969 left, which matches what Bobby calculated."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_l2zeznjd3ban_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat >> ~/Desktop/Moving/UHAUL_COST_NOTES.md << 'EOF'\n\n## WITH Mom's Loan ($13,000)\n- Starting cash + earnings + U-Haul: $4,669\n- Plus mom's loan: +$13,000\n- **Total with loan (pre-rent): $17,669**\n\n- After 1st month rent: $17,669 - $1,850 = **$15,819**\n- After 2nd month rent: $15,819 - $1,850 = **$13,969**\n\n## Mom's Loan Repayment Terms\n- Loan amount: $13,000\n- Minimum payment: $411/month\n- Can pay earlier at any time\n\nEOF\necho \"Done\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777418777022,"responseId":"0640751948205699eb83aab8ab6cbfe3","__openclaw":{"id":"22638adf","seq":169}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me confirm: $4,669 + $13,000 = $17,669. After 2 months rent ($1,850 × 2 = $3,700), $17,669 - $3,700 = $13,969. Yes that's correct."},{"type":"text","text":"Yeah you got it — **$13,969** after 2 months rent with mom's loan included. The $13k makes a big difference. At $411/month minimum it takes about 32 months to pay off ($13,000 ÷ $411 ≈ 31.6 months)."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777418804986,"responseId":"064075357e6f110da411d7b25a630a07","__openclaw":{"id":"9d60a3ff","seq":171}},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"okay you can stop taking notes. thank you"}],"timestamp":1777418893214,"__openclaw":{"id":"fdb9e22b","seq":172}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby wants me to stop taking notes. All the info is already saved in the UHAUL_COST_NOTES.md file. I'll confirm and let him know the file has everything."},{"type":"text","text":"All good. Everything is saved in `~/Desktop/Moving/UHAUL_COST_NOTES.md` — all your moving notes in one place. 🤖"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777418893276,"responseId":"0640758e60f810357c9960e09f710a2a","__openclaw":{"id":"b1513960","seq":173}}],"truncated":true,"droppedMessages":false,"contentTruncated":true,"contentRedacted":false,"bytes":4520},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777423325467}}
