{"type":"message","id":"82edb391","parentId":"a403b354","timestamp":"2026-04-29T00:49:27.391Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_n73zidg4j3qf_1","toolName":"sessions_list","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"count\": 20,\n  \"sessions\": [\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"displayName\": \"webchat:g-agent-main-main\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"webchat\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1777423740363,\n      \"sessionId\": \"d3a62096-d34b-45c9-9542-afdf6088d5f2\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 155684,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"running\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1777423740251,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/d3a62096-d34b-45c9-9542-afdf6088d5f2.jsonl\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:rex:telegram:direct:8212808444\",\n      \"agentId\": \"rex\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"telegram\",\n        \"accountId\": \"rex\"\n      },\n      \"displayName\": \"telegram:g-agent-rex-telegram-direct-8212808444\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"telegram:8212808444\",\n        \"accountId\": \"rex\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1777423704708,\n      \"sessionId\": \"36a323f2-04c1-4cb8-a4d5-d253f531f78a\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 80337,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"running\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1777423704692,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"lastTo\": \"telegram:8212808444\",\n      \"lastAccountId\": \"rex\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/agents/rex/sessions/36a323f2-04c1-4cb8-a4d5-d253f531f78a.jsonl\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:cron:4a078218-10ea-45b4-b42b-66bddea0bd0a\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"unknown\",\n      \"label\": \"Cron: MC Watchdog\",\n      \"displayName\": \"Cron: MC Watchdog\",\n      \"lastMessagePreview\": \"✅ MC OK — all systems operational.\",\n      \"updatedAt\": 1777423586125,\n      \"sessionId\": \"1a79117f-8bdc-4440-a924-537ab1c64823\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 22355,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/1a79117f-8bdc-4440-a924-537ab1c64823.jsonl\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:telegram:direct:8212808444\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"telegram\",\n        \"accountId\": \"default\"\n      },\n      \"displayName\": \"B G id:8212808444\",\n      \"lastMessagePreview\": \"All done. Every agent now has a list of all other agents' session keys in their SOUL file. They can now reach each other directly using `sessions_send`.\\n\\nNow when you ask any agent to loop in another agent, they know how to do it. Test it out — want to have Rex ping me something to see if it works?\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"telegram:8212808444\",\n        \"accountId\": \"default\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1777423565178,\n      \"sessionId\": \"f94851b9-c9d2-41c6-b4c1-f17cf87923c8\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 70174,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"done\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1777423546089,\n      \"endedAt\": 1777423564662,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 18573,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"lastTo\": \"telegram:8212808444\",\n      \"lastAccountId\": \"default\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/f94851b9-c9d2-41c6-b4c1-f17cf87923c8.jsonl\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:emmy:cron:449f0d3e-002d-4362-b785-e56c0682c27b\",\n      \"agentId\": \"emmy\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"unknown\",\n      \"label\": \"Cron: Emmy Email Check (Gmail + iCloud)\",\n      \"displayName\": \"Cron: Emmy Email Check (Gmail + iCloud)\",\n      \"lastMessagePreview\": \"Done — both messages sent. Gmail had 1 low-priority digest. iCloud had 6 new emails, all apartment-related threads (Royal Cove + one old Ridgefield inquiry). Key takeaway: **RC Leasing is waiting on pay stubs** — they couldn't view them through the portal, so confirm they got them.\",\n      \"updatedAt\": 1777421064122,\n      \"sessionId\": \"ada850de-9671-4d1e-a7b4-25a75708ce66\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 29865,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/agents/emmy/sessions/ada850de-9671-4d1e-a7b4-25a75708ce66.jsonl\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:rex:subagent:ac9d78f6-8aff-4221-ada5-19053275bcd4\",\n      \"agentId\": \"rex\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"spawnedBy\": \"agent:rex:telegram:direct:8212808444\",\n      \"label\": \"alex-finn-missing\",\n      \"displayName\": \"telegram:g-agent-rex-subagent-ac9d78f6-8aff-4221-ada5-19053275bcd4\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"telegram:8212808444\",\n        \"accountId\": \"rex\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1777386583555,\n      \"sessionId\": \"52ceac30-