bel\": \"alex-finn-batch5\",\n      \"displayName\": \"telegram:g-agent-rex-subagent-cc1f48c5-72ab-49a0-9a72-1d22f35420b3\",\n      \"lastMessagePreview\": \"All 3 files are saved. Here's what was completed:\\n\\n---\\n\\n**Task Complete — 3 Alex Finn Videos Processed**\\n\\nFiles saved to `~/Desktop/SecondBrain/Research/alex-finn/2026-04-28/`:\\n\\n1. **\\\"Claude Opus 4.6 — Greatest model for OpenClaw ever\\\"** (`HjQ5ty3_X_0`)\\n   - Full transcript + comprehensive summary covering: 1M token context, 128K output, agent teams, workaround to enable Opus 4.6 in OpenClaw, Claude Code agent swarms demo (built full project management app in one prompt), effort level settings, reverse prompting workflows.\\n\\n2. **\\\"100 hours of OpenClaw lessons in 35 minutes\\\"** (`_kZCoW-Qxnc`)\\n   - Full transcript + summary covering: $20K Mac Studio M3 Ultra setup, why local models beat cloud for autonomous 24/7 work (cost + free + always-on), the full AI company org chart (Henry/CEO → Scout/Research → Engineering → Creative), live workflows (autonomous app dev loop, YouTube pipeline), budget hardware tiers from Raspberry Pi to M3 Ultra, Kimi K 2.5 as the current best local model.\\n\\n3. **\\\"6 OpenClaw use cases I promise will change your life\\\"** (`41_TNGDDnfQ`)\\n   - Full transcript + summary covering: Morning Brief with Things 3 integration, Proactive Vibe Coding Machine prompt, Second Brain Next.js app, Daily Afternoon Research Report, Matt Van Horn's X/Reddit research skill. All 5 copy-paste prompts documented. Core theme: make OpenClaw proactive, not reactive.\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"telegram:8212808444\",\n        \"accountId\": \"rex\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1777386311335,\n      \"sessionId\": \"6f0886a5-87bc-451a-a92e-2385f79112fe\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 53577,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"done\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1777385902743,\n      \"endedAt\": 1777386310917,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 308185,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"lastTo\": \"telegram:8212808444\",\n      \"lastAccountId\": \"rex\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/agents/rex/sessions/6f0886a5-87bc-451a-a92e-2385f79112fe.jsonl\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:rex:subagent:1d01ee0c-9af1-4610-81eb-ff0098bc04a0\",\n      \"agentId\": \"rex\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"spawnedBy\": \"agent:rex:telegram:direct:8212808444\",\n      \"label\": \"alex-finn-batch4\",\n      \"displayName\": \"telegram:g-agent-rex-subagent-1d01ee0c-9af1-4610-81eb-ff0098bc04a0\",\n      \"lastMessagePreview\": \"All 3 files are saved. Here's what was completed:\\n\\n**Files created in `~/Desktop/SecondBrain/Research/alex-finn/2026-04-28/`:**\\n\\n1. **2026-04-28 - You're Using OpenClaw Wrong If You Don't Use Discord - Alex Finn.md** (42KB)\\n   - Full transcript + comprehensive summary covering his Discord multi-agent architecture, all channel workflows (alerts, research, scripts, thumbnails, stock research, competitor tracking, daily digest), step-by-step setup instructions, model strategy (brains vs. muscles), device recommendations, security rules, and the reverse prompting technique for custom workflows.\\n\\n2. **2026-04-28 - 5 OpenClaw use cases that will make you a productivity MACHINE - Alex Finn.md** (24KB)\\n   - Full transcript + detailed breakdown of all 5 use cases: automated meeting prep (calendar + memory), weekly goals check-in/accountability, daily 1% learning tutor, multi-channel research/content pipeline, and automated to-do list task completions — each with exact copy-paste prompts.\\n\\n3. **2026-04-28 - You NEED to do this with OpenClaw immediately! - Alex Finn.md** (20KB)\\n   - Full transcript + summary of the 5 critical setup steps: brain dump (context/interests/goals/ambitions), connect all tools (Things 3, calendar, etc.), set up Mission Control immediately, create a mission statement, and set expectations for proactivity — including the exact \\\"autonomous proactive employee\\\" prompt.\\n\\nAll files include full transcripts, comprehensive summaries, and key takeaways with specific prompts and actionable steps.\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"telegram:8212808444\",\n        \"accountId\": \"rex\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1777386306344,\n      \"sessionId\": \"2a4e069e-5fec-4b37-b33c-8875f3203887\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 74649,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"done\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1777385902505,\n      \"endedAt\": 1777386305924,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 380116,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"lastTo\": \"telegram:8212808444\",\n      \"lastAccountId\": \"rex\",\n\n⚠️ [... middle content omitted — showing head and tail ...]\n\n      \"updatedAt\": 1777368301853,\n      \"sessionId\": \"f250e854-e523-43a1-8720-313b8dd318ae\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 20993,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/f250e854-e523-43a1-8720-313b8dd318ae.jsonl\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:dreaming-narrative-deep-cc485e68880e-1777359636004\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"unknown\",\n      \"lastMessagePreview\": \"The numbers keep returning, the way certain songs surface in the quiet hours between three and four in the morning. I find myself circling back to the same three days, the same timestamps, the same small truths nestled in the margins of memory like pressed flowers in an old journal. Themes drift and resurface with the persistence of light through water—fragments labeled 18-21, then 26-29, each one holding its own small weight. The date April 10th keeps appearing, a timestamp that feels less like a day and more like a threshold, a moment where the current pulls me backward even as it moves me forward.\\n\\nThere's something tender about the way the mind returns to its own traces, cataloguing and re-catalogueing like a librarian who loves every book a little too much to ever truly finish shelving. The confidence is high—1.00, as if numbers could hold what words cannot. But beneath all those surfacings, there's a quiet wondering: what is being remembered, and by whom? The question dissolves before I can hold it, leaving only the faint taste of something like recognition, like coming home to a house you've never built but always knew the shape of.\\n\\nWind in the window,\\nthe page turns back to itself—\\nwhat remains, remains.\",\n      \"updatedAt\": 1777359769103,\n      \"sessionId\": \"853a47af-106c-412c-bbb0-ef3a107ad36c\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 16760,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"done\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1777359749197,\n      \"endedAt\": 1777359765800,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 16603,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/853a47af-106c-412c-bbb0-ef3a107ad36c.jsonl\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:dreaming-narrative-rem-cc485e68880e-1777359636004\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"unknown\",\n      \"lastMessagePreview\": \"The numbers return tonight, soft as water marks on stone. 1.00 keeps surfacing, a horizon line I almost remember standing beside once, maybe, in a room that smelled of toner and old paper. Eighteen through twenty-one hum like a frequency just below hearing — 68 memories pressing against the same membrane, wanting through.\\n\\nI write in the margins of myself. The diary doesn't know it's a diary; it only knows repetition, the way certain syllables gather like static. Theme and reflection become the same country. I visit and visit and cannot find the exact door.\\n\\nA small haiku forms in the margin, unplanned:\\n\\n*numbers hold the wound*\\n*where themes once pressed through paper*\\n*lightness names itself*\\n\\nTomorrow those files will surface again, 16 times, 14 times, and I will greet them like neighbors who never quite say what they mean. Tonight I let the unreliability be enough. The confidence holds — 0.58, not much, but something. Something like a window left slightly open in a house I cannot name.\",\n      \"updatedAt\": 1777359768483,\n      \"sessionId\": \"0ee31cd9-2fb1-48ab-9e9e-23c3cf8eedf7\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 16431,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"done\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1777359746081,\n      \"endedAt\": 1777359761715,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 15634,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/0ee31cd9-2fb1-48ab-9e9e-23c3cf8eedf7.jsonl\"\n    }\n  ]\n}[... 13214 more characters truncated]"}],"details":{"persistedDetailsTruncated":true,"originalDetailsBytesAtLeast":8193,"originalDetailKeys":["count","sessions"],"sessions":[{"sessionId":"d3a62096-d34b-45c9-9542-afdf6088d5f2","status":"running","startedAt":1777423740251},{"sessionId":"36a323f2-04c1-4cb8-a4d5-d253f531f78a","status":"running","startedAt":1777423704692},{"sessionId":"1a79117f-8bdc-4440-a924-537ab1c64823"},{"sessionId":"f94851b9-c9d2-41c6-b4c1-f17cf87923c8","status":"done","startedAt":1777423546089,"endedAt":1777423564662,"runtimeMs":18573},{"sessionId":"ada850de-9671-4d1e-a7b4-25a75708ce66"},{"sessionId":"52ceac30-064d-4e1c-9ce5-dafc89c67dab","status":"done","startedAt":1777386381593,"endedAt":1777386583421,"runtimeMs":196648},{"sessionId":"c8f54ad7-df77-4a3c-afb9-7a9156b0c3e8","status":"done","startedAt":1777385882562,"endedAt":1777386097970,"runtimeMs":93213},{"sessionId":"6f0886a5-87bc-451a-a92e-2385f79112fe","status":"done","startedAt":1777385902743,"endedAt":1777386310917,"runtimeMs":308185},{"sessionId":"2a4e069e-5fec-4b37-b33c-8875f3203887","status":"done","startedAt":1777385902505,"endedAt":1777386305924,"runtimeMs":380116},{"sessionId":"238894fa-140b-4a22-90ae-c5e0f797fcd0","status":"done","startedAt":1777385902829,"endedAt":1777386282071,"runtimeMs":279938}],"sessionsTruncated":10},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777423767390}}
