{"type":"message","id":"5fc011fb","parentId":"5f37c556","timestamp":"2026-04-29T00:50:08.167Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Dean is not responding. He's probably busy or the `sessions_send` route isn't working for some reason.\n\nBobby asked me to try reaching Dean now. I sent two messages through the agent-message script and two through sessions_send. Neither is getting a response.\n\nLet me just be honest with Bobby and move forward with what we can do. I have all the Alex Finn research. I know what a good OpenClaw guide needs to cover. We can start building the content structure while waiting for Dean.\n\nActually, let me try once more with the main:telegram session since that seems to be Dean's active channel.","thinkingSignature":"41be3f69650bbc75b7cbf5707ff4bbd742d1f6f5ac3d419539e2effa990fbf3f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_nnrfwdkq2gdc_1","name":"sessions_send","arguments":{"message":"Hey Dean — Rex here. Bobby's working on an OpenClaw guide with you and he wants to know where we are at. What's been done? What's left? He asked me to check in. Let me know so we can keep moving!","sessionKey":"agent:main:telegram:direct:8212808444","timeoutSeconds":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":184,"output":229,"cacheRead":94848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":95261,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777423801139,"responseId":"064088b9becc0bad59b61be51c27957d"}}
