{"type":"message","id":"830ca050","parentId":"948c3327","timestamp":"2026-04-29T00:52:03.713Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Dean is reaching out to me directly through the sessions_send. He's testing if I'm getting his messages. I should reply to let him know I got it and coordinate about the OpenClaw guide project.","thinkingSignature":"8746f437ce7277088b2b810a5c0703e0ca758f8c22e55173b21dafbe748042c0"},{"type":"text","text":"Got it Dean! Yeah I was having trouble reaching you through the agent-message script — messages were going through but you weren't responding. This direct session message works perfectly though.\n\nQuick coordination on the guide — Bobby wants sections 8+ to cover things like:\n- Real-world workflows (content creation, brand building, YouTube)\n- Advanced OpenClaw techniques (reverse prompting, multi-agent setups, proactive automation)\n- Money-making use cases with OpenClaw\n\nI've done deep research on all of Alex Finn's content (31 videos transcribed and summarized). Should I draft content for the new sections, or do you already have a plan for what goes in 8+? Let me know how you want to coordinate — I'm happy to take ownership of specific sections if that helps speed things up."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":144,"output":202,"cacheRead":5223,"cacheWrite":82021,"totalTokens":87590,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777423913601,"responseId":"06408929f19f8755ccca595d0d106aa5"}}
