{"type":"message","id":"e7991944","parentId":"dd768bc5","timestamp":"2026-04-29T00:57:53.045Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_103g48bib5bf_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"-rw-------@ 1 bobbygalletta  staff   6684 Apr 27 22:45 /Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/OpenClaw/OpenClaw-Guide-By-Bobby/Section-1-What-is-OpenClaw.md\n-rw-------  1 bobbygalletta  staff  12260 Apr 28 20:57 /Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/OpenClaw/OpenClaw-Guide-By-Bobby/Section-10-Money-Making-Use-Cases.md\n-rw-------@ 1 bobbygalletta  staff   6881 Apr 27 22:45 /Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/OpenClaw/OpenClaw-Guide-By-Bobby/Section-2-Why-OpenClaw-Over-ChatGPT.md\n-rw-------@ 1 bobbygalletta  staff   9007 Apr 27 22:47 /Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/OpenClaw/OpenClaw-Guide-By-Bobby/Section-3-How-OpenClaw-Has-Benefited-Me.md\n-rw-------  1 bobbygalletta  staff  10265 Apr 27 22:48 /Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/OpenClaw/OpenClaw-Guide-By-Bobby/Section-4-Things-I-Wish-I-Knew.md\n-rw-------  1 bobbygalletta  staff  11026 Apr 27 22:49 /Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/OpenClaw/OpenClaw-Guide-By-Bobby/Section-5-Installation-Setup.md\n-rw-------@ 1 bobbygalletta  staff  11498 Apr 27 22:49 /Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/OpenClaw/OpenClaw-Guide-By-Bobby/Section-6-Core-Concepts.md\n-rw-------  1 bobbygalletta  staff   9180 Apr 27 22:50 /Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/OpenClaw/OpenClaw-Guide-By-Bobby/Section-7-Your-First-Automation.md\n-rw-------  1 bobbygalletta  staff  11371 Apr 28 20:54 /Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/OpenClaw/OpenClaw-Guide-By-Bobby/Section-8-Real-World-Workflows.md\n-rw-------  1 bobbygalletta  staff  12463 Apr 28 20:56 /Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/OpenClaw/OpenClaw-Guide-By-Bobby/Section-9-Advanced-Techniques.md"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":50,"aggregated":"-rw-------@ 1 bobbygalletta  staff   6684 Apr 27 22:45 /Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/OpenClaw/OpenClaw-Guide-By-Bobby/Section-1-What-is-OpenClaw.md\n-rw-------  1 bobbygalletta  staff  12260 Apr 28 20:57 /Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/OpenClaw/OpenClaw-Guide-By-Bobby/Section-10-Money-Making-Use-Cases.md\n-rw-------@ 1 bobbygalletta  staff   6881 Apr 27 22:45 /Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/OpenClaw/OpenClaw-Guide-By-Bobby/Section-2-Why-OpenClaw-Over-ChatGPT.md\n-rw-------@ 1 bobbygalletta  staff   9007 Apr 27 22:47 /Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/OpenClaw/OpenClaw-Guide-By-Bobby/Section-3-How-OpenClaw-Has-Benefited-Me.md\n-rw-------  1 bobbygalletta  staff  10265 Apr 27 22:48 /Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/OpenClaw/OpenClaw-Guide-By-Bobby/Section-4-Things-I-Wish-I-Knew.md\n-rw-------  1 bobbygalletta  staff  11026 Apr 27 22:49 /Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/OpenClaw/OpenClaw-Guide-By-Bobby/Section-5-Installation-Setup.md\n-rw-------@ 1 bobbygalletta  staff  11498 Apr 27 22:49 /Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/OpenClaw/OpenClaw-Guide-By-Bobby/Section-6-Core-Concepts.md\n-rw-------  1 bobbygalletta  staff   9180 Apr 27 22:50 /Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/OpenClaw/OpenClaw-Guide-By-Bobby/Section-7-Your-First-Automation.md\n-rw-------  1 bobbygalletta  staff  11371 Apr 28 20:54 /Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/OpenClaw/OpenClaw-Guide-By-Bobby/Section-8-Real-World-Workflows.md\n-rw-------  1 bobbygalletta  staff  12463 Apr 28 20:56 /Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/OpenClaw/OpenClaw-Guide-By-Bobby/Section-9-Advanced-Techniques.md","cwd":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-rex"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777424273045}}
{"type":"message","id":"a230883c","parentId":"e7991944","timestamp":"2026-04-29T00:58:02.528Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All three sections are written. Let me notify Dean that they're done.\n","thinkingSignature":"6488527ba4bd4f484309b3bff6fa271c6ab07fb1ccd31a6beefaf91f0f9d1424"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nDean — Sections 8, 9, and 10 are done and saved to the guide folder.\n\nHere's what was written:\n\n**Section 8: Real-World Workflows** (11.3KB)\n- YouTube Research Pipeline\n- AI-Powered Script Writing\n- Content Repurposing Machine\n- Personal Brand Management\n- YouTube Channel Operations (Multi-Agent)\n- Music & Brand Building\n- Quick-start guide for picking which workflow to start with\n\n**Section 9: Advanced Techniques** (12.5KB)\n- Reverse Prompting\n- Brain Dump + Expectation Setting Combo\n- Building Your Own Tooling\n- Multi-Agent Architectures\n- The Heartbeat Trick (cost cutting)\n- Memory Flush (5-second fix)\n- Prompting Your Prompts meta-technique\n\n**Section 10: Money-Making Use Cases** (12.2KB)\n- Sell Your OpenClaw Expertise (consulting, guides, templates)\n- Content Creation Machine (YouTube monetization)\n- Build and Sell Digital Products\n- Services Business Powered by OpenClaw\n- Build a YouTube Channel Around AI Tools\n- OpenClaw-Powered Music Career\n- Affiliate Marketing with AI Tools\n- Force Multiplication principle tying it all together\n\nTotal new content: ~36KB across 3 sections. Ready for your review and compile pass. Let me know if you need any edits or want me to adjust the angle on anything."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":634,"output":310,"cacheRead":98048,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98992,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777424273048,"responseId":"06408a91ff85c738625949e2c360854a"}}
